WEBVTT

00:00:18.838 --> 00:00:20.708
[Yamato] Getting ready
for the storm?

00:00:27.589 --> 00:00:30.327
Man. This little guy
really likes you, Mei.

00:00:30.427 --> 00:00:32.933
I didn't think anyone
saw me out here, yanno,

00:00:33.033 --> 00:00:35.237
this part of the courtyard
being so far away.

00:00:35.337 --> 00:00:37.341
Well, I saw you just fine.

00:00:43.854 --> 00:00:46.660
Your hair seems a little
frizzier than usual today.

00:00:46.760 --> 00:00:50.000
It must be the rain.
I should get it cut soon.

00:00:50.100 --> 00:00:51.604
Can I go with you?!

00:00:51.704 --> 00:00:54.041
Oh? Huh?

00:00:58.517 --> 00:01:02.792
<i>Today I, Mei Tachibana,</i>
<i>am quite flustered.</i>

00:01:02.892 --> 00:01:06.934
<i>I'm about to go out with a boy</i>
<i>for the very first time...</i>

00:01:07.034 --> 00:01:09.640
<i>in my life. Oh my god.</i>

00:02:52.812 --> 00:02:54.382
Late, Tachibana?

00:02:54.482 --> 00:02:55.918
That's not a good way to start.

00:02:56.019 --> 00:02:58.524
It takes a lot of nerve to run
twenty minutes late for our

00:02:58.624 --> 00:03:00.795
first date without
calling me, yanno.

00:03:02.297 --> 00:03:04.268
Whatever.

00:03:04.368 --> 00:03:07.074
We're going to the
salon, not dating.

00:03:07.174 --> 00:03:09.946
Of course this is a date.

00:03:10.047 --> 00:03:15.190
<i>[Mei] Honestly, it's not</i>
<i>that I don't want to go</i>
<i>on a date with him...</i>

00:03:15.290 --> 00:03:19.065
<i>I actually did worry</i>
<i>about what to wear...</i>

00:03:19.165 --> 00:03:21.770
This? Or maybe this...

00:03:23.406 --> 00:03:26.780
No, I don't want to go out
there looking too dressed up.

00:03:26.880 --> 00:03:28.517
Where are you off to?

00:03:28.617 --> 00:03:30.688
[Mei] Uh, the salon.
[Ms. Tachibana] My goodness.

00:03:30.788 --> 00:03:34.295
Why would you get all dressed up
for something like a haircut?

00:03:34.395 --> 00:03:36.867
Now wait a minute! Mei-chan!

00:03:36.967 --> 00:03:38.369
You've got a date!

00:03:38.470 --> 00:03:42.144
No, I'm just going to the
salon. Stop dancing like that!

00:03:42.244 --> 00:03:43.814
You go girl!

00:03:45.317 --> 00:03:49.258
But, it's... I said
it's not really... Mom!

00:03:50.260 --> 00:03:53.501
<i>I swore to myself that</i>
<i>this isn't a date,</i>

00:03:53.601 --> 00:03:56.740
<i>which is why when</i>
<i>I chose my outfit,</i>

00:03:56.840 --> 00:03:59.311
<i>I ended up with this.</i>

00:03:59.412 --> 00:04:01.784
Look at that. We're
even dressed alike.

00:04:01.884 --> 00:04:05.323
Looks like we have the
same taste in clothes.
That's pretty cool.

00:04:06.894 --> 00:04:11.904
Oh, hey! Nakanishi just
told me that he and Asami
just started going out.

00:04:12.004 --> 00:04:13.574
Oh. I'm glad.

00:04:13.674 --> 00:04:15.177
He said it was thanks to you.

00:04:15.277 --> 00:04:17.347
I didn't do anything really.

00:04:17.448 --> 00:04:19.719
[Yamato] Nakanishi
called you amazing.

00:04:19.820 --> 00:04:21.122
You know something?

00:04:21.222 --> 00:04:24.028
I'm happy for him. Now.

00:04:24.128 --> 00:04:26.165
We need to get to the salon.

00:04:26.265 --> 00:04:28.136
Now? We can go later.

00:04:28.236 --> 00:04:30.173
Unless you have an appointment?

00:04:30.273 --> 00:04:31.409
I don't, but...

00:04:31.510 --> 00:04:33.246
Then let's have some fun first.

00:04:33.346 --> 00:04:35.785
We can go to the
salon later, 'kay?

00:04:35.885 --> 00:04:37.321
Yeah, sure.

00:04:37.421 --> 00:04:38.691
[Yamato] Where should we go?

00:04:38.791 --> 00:04:40.460
A movie? Karaoke?

00:04:40.561 --> 00:04:42.699
N-Nowhere behind closed
doors, got it?!

00:04:42.799 --> 00:04:45.036
[Yamato] Why not?
[Mei] Well, because...

00:04:48.042 --> 00:04:49.646
Ha, don't worry about that.

00:04:49.746 --> 00:04:52.151
I won't do anything
besides kiss you anyway.

00:04:52.251 --> 00:04:53.319
[Mei] Say what?!

00:04:53.419 --> 00:04:55.691
[Girl 1] Hey, that
guy is super hot!

00:04:55.791 --> 00:04:58.062
[Girl 2] Totally hot!
I bet he's a model.

00:04:58.163 --> 00:05:00.668
[Girl 1] Should we talk to him?
[Girl 2] He's with a girl.

00:05:00.768 --> 00:05:02.505
[Girl 1] There's no way
she's his girlfriend.

00:05:02.605 --> 00:05:05.878
[Girl 2] Well, let's
try talking to him then!

00:05:05.978 --> 00:05:08.951
[Talent Scout] Excuse me,
do you have a moment?

00:05:09.051 --> 00:05:12.124
Sorry to spring this on
you, but I work for a
talent agency and I was-

00:05:12.224 --> 00:05:16.567
[Yamato] I'm not interested
in that kind of thing. Sorry.

00:05:20.675 --> 00:05:21.844
[Girl 3] Check him out.

00:05:21.944 --> 00:05:26.485
[Girl 4] He's so handsome.

00:05:26.587 --> 00:05:28.289
Mei, is something wrong?

00:05:28.389 --> 00:05:32.932
No, I was just wondering if
this is the way people
always act around you.

00:05:33.032 --> 00:05:33.901
Huh?

00:05:34.001 --> 00:05:35.470
[Mei] Getting scouted...

00:05:35.571 --> 00:05:38.142
Girls just walking
up to you like that.

00:05:38.243 --> 00:05:42.451
Uuuh... The talent scout?
