to be seen with me.

00:05:52.772 --> 00:05:55.778
Mei-san, do I look
that shallow to you?

00:05:57.180 --> 00:06:01.890
I really don't know
what to think. It's a
lot for me to take in.

00:06:02.357 --> 00:06:04.028
I see.

00:06:06.600 --> 00:06:08.871
Let's act more like
a couple, okay?

00:06:08.971 --> 00:06:12.779
I mean, we're on a date, and we
don't need anymore distractions.

00:06:14.749 --> 00:06:17.522
[Mei] But we haven't
started dating...

00:06:17.622 --> 00:06:19.024
[Yamato] Sure we have.

00:06:20.193 --> 00:06:22.130
You're my girlfriend now.

00:06:25.136 --> 00:06:30.815
<i>[Mei] I thought holding</i>
<i>someone's hand wasn't as</i>
<i>big a deal as kissing, but...</i>

00:06:30.915 --> 00:06:36.325
<i>As our hands touched,</i>
<i>I could feel his warmth</i>
<i>in a different way,</i>

00:06:36.425 --> 00:06:39.933
<i>but it made my heart</i>
<i>pound just as hard.</i>

00:06:40.033 --> 00:06:44.809
<i>I really didn't know another</i>
<i>person's touch could be so</i>
<i>warm, and comforting.</i>

00:06:45.578 --> 00:06:46.947
<i>It was nice.</i>

00:06:50.253 --> 00:06:52.024
[Masashi] Yamato!

00:06:55.865 --> 00:06:57.067
It is you.

00:06:59.071 --> 00:07:00.407
