00:07:00.508 --> 00:07:02.545
[Yamato] Hey, Masashi.
Aiko-chan.

00:07:02.645 --> 00:07:05.317
You guys make an odd
couple, you know that?

00:07:05.417 --> 00:07:07.555
[Yamato] First date.

00:07:08.056 --> 00:07:08.624
No way?!

00:07:08.724 --> 00:07:10.160
Well uh, we just...

00:07:10.260 --> 00:07:12.565
Me and Aiko we're about to
head to the bowling alley.

00:07:12.665 --> 00:07:14.703
You wanna come with?

00:07:14.803 --> 00:07:17.542
[Yamato] Should we?
[Mei] I really need to
get my hair cut.

00:07:17.642 --> 00:07:21.382
[Aiko] Come with us.
We have extra coupons.

00:07:21.482 --> 00:07:23.954
