fun with four.

00:07:25.524 --> 00:07:26.927
Alright.

00:07:27.027 --> 00:07:27.996
[Yamato] You sure?

00:07:28.096 --> 00:07:29.498
[Mei] Yeah.

00:07:33.272 --> 00:07:37.381
[Masashi] The teams are
gonna be me and Aiko against
Yamato and Tachibana!

00:07:37.481 --> 00:07:39.151
You're on!

00:07:39.251 --> 00:07:45.130
<i>[Aiko] Why the hell would</i>
<i>Yamato choose someone</i>
<i>like Tachibana?</i>

00:07:45.230 --> 00:07:47.735
<i>What's so good about her?</i>

00:07:48.570 --> 00:07:51.943
Pins. Your days are numbered.

