00:07:57.755 --> 00:08:00.393
[Yamato laughs] You're up, Mei.

00:08:00.493 --> 00:08:02.397
[Mei] O-okay.

00:08:02.497 --> 00:08:05.236
[Yamato] I got your back,
so just do your best.

00:08:06.740 --> 00:08:09.713
This is the first time I've
seen Tachibana even move.

00:08:09.813 --> 00:08:12.150
