00:08:24.441 --> 00:08:26.780
[Aiko] A-A strike?!

00:08:27.749 --> 00:08:29.519
[Yamato] That was awesome, Mei!

00:08:29.619 --> 00:08:30.588
[Masashi] Who are you?!

00:08:30.688 --> 00:08:32.558
[Yamato] You're good at bowling?

00:08:32.658 --> 00:08:36.265
