00:08:51.262 --> 00:08:54.435
[Yamato] Now punch it in!
[Masashi] Aiko, I think you and
I are gonna lose real bad.

00:08:54.536 --> 00:08:56.205
Yeah!

00:08:56.305 --> 00:09:00.080
<i>[Aiko] What the hell?</i>
<i>Yamato looks like he's</i>
<i>really having fun.</i>

00:09:00.180 --> 00:09:03.721
The boy looks smitten...
with Tachibana no less.

00:09:03.821 --> 00:09:07.595
But I'm head over
heels for you, Aiko!

00:09:07.695 --> 00:09:09.899
[Aiko] Hearing that does
not make me happy.

00:09:09.999 --> 00:09:11.135
Ack!

00:09:12.204 --> 00:09:13.907
[Aiko] This is annoying.

00:09:18.216 --> 00:09:19.819
Tachibana.

00:09:20.588 --> 00:09:22.324
Let's hit the soda machine.

00:09:24.896 --> 00:09:28.469
So tell me, did you call
Yamato or did he call you?

00:09:28.570 --> 00:09:29.572
Why are you guys out today?

00:09:29.672 --> 00:09:31.777
I didn't ask him.

00:09:31.877 --> 00:09:34.649
When I told him I needed
to go the salon today,

00:09:34.749 --> 00:09:37.087
he just kind of invited
himself along, yanno.

00:09:37.187 --> 00:09:38.590
He invited himself?

00:09:38.690 --> 00:09:40.728
Aren't you guys already
dating or something?

00:09:40.828 --> 00:09:44.201
