tell me that we are, but...

00:09:44.301 --> 00:09:47.073
I don't know what it means
to dating someone yet.

00:09:47.174 --> 00:09:48.844
It's so new to me.

00:09:50.013 --> 00:09:53.954
Okay, Tachibana. Do you
like Yamato, or don't you?

00:09:56.091 --> 00:09:57.060
