you're guessing and trying
to make up your mind?

00:10:12.157 --> 00:10:14.361
So answer me this.

00:10:14.461 --> 00:10:18.136
Why would he choose
you over someone he's
already had sex with?

00:10:21.041 --> 00:10:24.983
So, if you're not sure about
him, stop wasting his time.

00:10:30.895 --> 00:10:32.130
[Yamato] Where's Mei?

00:10:32.230 --> 00:10:33.399
[Aiko] No clue.

00:10:34.268 --> 00:10:36.138
Uh, Mei!

00:10:36.238 --> 00:10:37.875
You're up next, okay?

00:10:41.583 --> 00:10:43.152
[Yamato] Get us
another strike, Mei!

00:10:52.304 --> 00:10:53.406
Mei?

00:11:00.888 --> 00:11:02.725
[Mei] I'm going home.

00:11:06.332 --> 00:11:08.236
Hey! Mei!

00:11:08.336 --> 00:11:12.010
Let her go. Stay and hang out
with me and Masashi, okay?

00:11:12.110 --> 00:11:15.216
Look, Aiko. I'm with
Mei today, alright?

00:11:15.316 --> 00:11:16.418
Sorry.

00:11:18.456 --> 00:11:19.859
Mei!

00:11:36.693 --> 00:11:38.162
Mei!

00:11:44.976 --> 00:11:49.117
So, Aiko-chan. If you're
not angry anymore...

00:11:49.218 --> 00:11:51.388
I'm gettin' kind of
hungry over here.

00:11:51.488 --> 00:11:52.658
Really not up for it.

00:11:52.758 --> 00:11:54.294
I know you still
like him and all,

00:11:54.394 --> 00:11:55.564
but you've got me.

00:11:55.664 --> 00:11:57.000
No way. I'm not letting that

00:11:57.100 --> 00:11:59.371
mousey little thing beat me.

00:11:59.471 --> 00:12:01.475
You're talking about Tachibana?

00:12:01.576 --> 00:12:06.285
<i>[Aiko] What's so good about</i>
<i>that ugly, loudmouthed bitch</i>
<i>who didn't even try?</i>

00:12:06.385 --> 00:12:10.928
<i>I'd do anything for the</i>
<i>man that I love. Anything.</i>

00:12:12.698 --> 00:12:15.403
[Girl 1] Aiko, are you ready?

00:12:15.504 --> 00:12:18.543
Sorry, I have a
date with my guy.

00:12:18.644 --> 00:12:19.478
[Girl 2] Oh?

00:12:19.579 --> 00:12:21.015
Lucky.

00:12:21.115 --> 00:12:23.052
[Girl 1] So introduce
him to us next time.

00:12:23.152 --> 00:12:25.658
<i>[Aiko] With my last boyfriend,</i>

00:12:25.758 --> 00:12:31.201
<i>I devoted my time and money to</i>
<i>become the girl of his dreams.</i>

00:12:31.302 --> 00:12:35.577
<i>I bought all the makeup</i>
<i>and pills I could to</i>
<i>improve my looks.</i>

00:12:35.678 --> 00:12:41.455
<i>But the harder I tried,</i>
<i>the more I realized</i>
<i>it'd never be enough.</i>

00:12:41.556 --> 00:12:43.292
<i>In my pursuit of a quick fix,</i>

00:12:43.392 --> 00:12:46.065
<i>I ruined my skin.</i>

00:12:56.151 --> 00:12:59.559
[Yamato] You don't need
all that make-up, Aiko.

00:12:59.659 --> 00:13:03.165
You sure are putting in
a lot of work for that
boyfriend of yours.

00:13:06.438 --> 00:13:11.783
<i>[Aiko] It was the first time in</i>
<i>my life someone complimented</i>
<i>my natural looks.</i>

00:13:11.883 --> 00:13:15.858
<i>Yamato saw me for</i>
<i>who I really was.</i>

00:13:15.958 --> 00:13:19.297
<i>I liked it. That's why...</i>

00:13:25.009 --> 00:13:27.447
<i>When I found out my boyfriend</i>
<i>had cheated on me...</i>

00:13:28.416 --> 00:13:30.019
Yamato!

00:13:33.259 --> 00:13:36.065
I can't take it anymore!
I want to die!

00:13:36.165 --> 00:13:38.169
I tried so hard, but...

00:13:38.269 --> 00:13:41.609
I'll never be as cute as
other girls! I look stupid!

00:13:41.710 --> 00:13:42.812
How can you say that?

00:13:42.912 --> 00:13:44.716
Then have sex with me!

00:13:44.816 --> 00:13:46.452
Please, Yamato!

00:13:56.940 --> 00:14:00.480
<i>I took advantage of</i>
<i>Yamato's kindness.</i>

00:14:06.993 --> 00:14:09.431
<i>I lost weight for Yamato.</i>

00:14:09.532 --> 00:14:12.972
<i>44 pounds in two months.</i>

00:14:14.575 --> 00:14:18.249
<i>I just wanted to be beautiful.</i>

00:14:18.349 --> 00:14:21.288
<i>And I will not accept that he</i>
<i>would be with someone who wants</i>

00:14:21.388 --> 00:14:25.998
<i>to pussyfoot around him and</i>
<i>not put in the work it takes.</i>

00:15:12.725 --> 00:15:14.662
I thought I'd find you here.

00:15:30.694 --> 00:15:32.832
Did Aiko say something to you?

00:15:32.932 --> 00:15:36.673
Why would he choose
you over someone he's
already had sex with?

00:15:38.543 --> 00:15:42.317
[Mei] I don't understand
you, Kurosawa-kun.

00:15:43.854 --> 00:15:45.958
We're just too different.

00:15:48.797 --> 00:15:50.333
[Yamato] That's not true.

00:15:53.807 --> 00:15:55.944
[Mei] He likes you.

00:15:56.044 --> 00:15:58.249
