away a couple of times,

00:15:58.349 --> 00:16:02.157
but after a couple visits,
he finally warmed up to me.

00:16:08.302 --> 00:16:11.475
Mei-san. Can I show
you something?

00:16:23.767 --> 00:16:25.604
[Yamato] And we're here!

00:16:25.704 --> 00:16:27.240
[Mei] What is this place?

00:16:27.340 --> 00:16:29.044
[Yamato] My middle school.

00:16:29.645 --> 00:16:31.281
Takes me back!

00:17:01.108 --> 00:17:04.314
I put a hole in this
wall, with my fist.

00:17:04.414 --> 00:17:08.055
I guess you could say
I was pretty wild.

