up a target, I kept a close
eye on everyone around me.

00:17:32.437 --> 00:17:35.142
Making sure I wasn't the
next guy to get hit.

00:17:36.646 --> 00:17:38.984
I was like a chameleon.

00:17:39.084 --> 00:17:42.190
I did my best to blend
in with my surroundings,

00:17:42.290 --> 00:17:44.695
doing and saying what
I needed to stay safe.

00:17:48.770 --> 00:17:52.477
One day, my best friend became
the bullies' next target.

00:17:52.578 --> 00:17:56.418
Around the other kids, I ignored
him like everyone else.

00:17:56.519 --> 00:17:59.625
Secretly, though,
we'd meet up to talk.

00:17:59.725 --> 00:18:03.098
I had some nerve acting
like a real friend to him.

00:18:03.198 --> 00:18:11.248
Even then, one day he came to
me, with his face covered in
bruises and he said,

00:18:11.348 --> 00:18:14.822
"I wanted to thank you for
talking to me, Kurosawa-kun."

00:18:15.757 --> 00:18:20.166
But the next day, he
transferred schools.

00:18:20.266 --> 00:18:23.740
I never really did anything
that truly helped him.

00:18:24.742 --> 00:18:25.844
Damn!

00:18:26.746 --> 00:18:28.850
Damn! Damn!

00:18:30.052 --> 00:18:31.756
Damn it!

00:18:37.768 --> 00:18:40.874
I never felt so useless.

00:18:42.243 --> 00:18:46.318
Mei, I know you think
we're worlds apart,

00:18:47.320 --> 00:18:48.823
but the truth is I...

00:18:49.792 --> 00:18:51.428
The truth is...

00:18:52.230 --> 00:18:54.034
Even now in high school,

00:18:54.134 --> 00:18:57.675
I'm still blending
in with the crowd.

00:18:57.775 --> 00:19:00.212
