00:19:01.516 --> 00:19:04.655
It isn't that at all.
From what I've seen,

00:19:04.755 --> 00:19:07.528
people seem to be naturally
attracted to you, you know.

00:19:07.628 --> 00:19:09.598
[Yamato] Sure, to my looks.
[Mei] Oh, come on!

00:19:09.699 --> 00:19:12.905
[Mei] You just can't get a
friendship with your looks.

00:19:13.005 --> 00:19:15.677
There's faith, and
trust, and work too.

00:19:17.146 --> 00:19:20.386
So now you're telling
me to trust people?

00:19:20.486 --> 00:19:23.960
Because you taught me to
think that way, Kurosawa-kun.

00:19:24.060 --> 00:19:26.398
I never thought I'd
say this, but...

00:19:26.498 --> 00:19:33.513
Little by little, bit by bit,
I want to start trusting people.

00:19:33.613 --> 00:19:36.351
Know what I think?
You're pretty strong.

00:19:36.451 --> 00:19:38.923
And because of that, people
don't push you around.

00:19:39.725 --> 00:19:41.261
I really like that.

00:19:41.996 --> 00:19:44.769
Mei, I...

00:19:50.379 --> 00:19:54.154
I fell in love with you
the moment you kicked me.

00:19:54.254 --> 00:19:56.859
I bet I seem a lot
less cool now.

00:19:58.630 --> 00:20:01.401
You've shown me your
vulnerability, Kurosawa-kun.

00:20:01.502 --> 00:20:03.640
To someone like me, that's cool.

00:20:08.683 --> 00:20:10.520
You know Mei,

00:20:10.620 --> 00:20:12.958
this might not be the
right time, but...

00:20:21.876 --> 00:20:23.378
Can I kiss you?

00:20:27.855 --> 00:20:29.390
[Mei] Sure.

00:20:47.160 --> 00:20:48.897
<i>[Mei] I know it</i>
<i>seems strange...</i>

00:20:48.997 --> 00:20:52.270
<i>but I was terrified of being</i>
<i>alone with him this morning,</i>

00:20:52.370 --> 00:20:55.744
<i>but now it feels</i>
<i>so comfortable.</i>

00:20:55.844 --> 00:20:58.550
[Mei] I can't go get
my hair cut now.

00:20:58.650 --> 00:21:00.954
[Yamato] It looks
better long anyway.

00:21:01.054 --> 00:21:03.192
[Mei] Then maybe
I won't cut it...

00:21:03.292 --> 00:21:04.227
[Yamato] Really?

00:21:04.327 --> 00:21:07.568
[Mei] I-I haven't decided yet!

00:21:07.668 --> 00:21:09.839
Well, I don't think you need to.

00:21:09.939 --> 00:21:12.410
It's cute the way it is.

00:21:14.682 --> 00:21:17.153
[Mei] If you give
people your trust...

00:21:17.253 --> 00:21:19.324
If you associate with people...

00:21:19.424 --> 00:21:24.602
You're going to have problems
you don't have when you stay in
your shell and don't come out.

00:21:26.939 --> 00:21:29.845
Just like I have my wounds,

00:21:29.945 --> 00:21:33.887
I learned that Kurosawa-kun
has his, too.

00:21:33.987 --> 00:21:37.895
So instead of hiding in my
shell, I'm going to stand up...

00:21:39.765 --> 00:21:41.569
and face them.

00:21:46.946 --> 00:21:48.550
[Masashi] Aiko?

00:21:51.856 --> 00:21:54.060
<i>[Aiko] I am not...</i>

00:21:54.160 --> 00:21:55.897
<i>letting it end like this.</i>

00:23:30.419 --> 00:23:35.530
My first time experiencing the
warmth of someone's hand was
so nice and reassuring.

00:23:35.630 --> 00:23:38.569
I hope I can truly come to
understand how wonderful it

00:23:38.670 --> 00:23:40.439
can be to actually
connect with others.

00:23:40.540 --> 00:23:42.109
[Marshmellow] Keep your
hands off my Mei,

00:23:42.209 --> 00:23:44.648
Yamato Kurosawa. Meow.

